<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ك ث ث:</span> <span class="c2">(كَثَّ)</span> الشَّيْءُ مِنْ بَابِ سَلِمَ أَيْ كَثُفَ. وَلِحْيَةٌ <span class="c2">(كَثَّةٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(كَثَّاءُ)</span> بِالْمَدِّ وَالتَّشْدِيدِ فِيهِمَا. وَرَجُلٌ <span class="c2">(كَثُّ)</span> اللِّحْيَةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>